{"tid":796920,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"FG要見工. 以前兼職工作證明點?","createTime":"2018-08-28T06:05:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-28T06:32:57.000Z","uid":58069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"69dda95df05a922854a150dc33f716fa34c62d3c","tid":796920,"uid":58069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T06:05:23.000Z","msg":"以前就做左幾份PART TIME. 之前見全職都冇話要帶工作證明.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次見銀行工就寫到明要<br />\nA printed copy of CV <br />\nCopies of job references (including internship, part-time and summer job references) <br />\nA completed application form as attached <br />\n等等<br />\n<br />\n咁我幾年前做過幾份垃圾 PART TIME . 得1份係有工作證明EMAIL左比我<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁我填表比佢果陣應唔應該寫埋果幾份垃圾PARTIME落去?<br />\n但係我SEND CV比佢果陣又填左果幾份PARTTIME落去。<br />\n<br />\n唔寫,得1份兼職又好似好少經驗,同埋send cv果陣又有寫，如果人地睇番見到有幾份PART TIME又好似講大話咁?<br />\n寫左,如果佢要我比工作證明咁比唔到又點搞?<br />\n銀行工又會唔會CHECK得特別嚴?<br />\n<br />\n求屌,新入職場完全唔識呢D野<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7037adcb3be9b213f2219bc45a706560a1f37fb4","tid":796920,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T06:06:21.000Z","msg":"稅單<br />\n糧單"},{"pid":"3ca63d80bf36957e4b29824d4dde035d60dd9a1e","tid":796920,"uid":61766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T06:07:24.000Z","msg":"你返part time 嗰陣無問佢攞工作證明？<br />\n有無糧單嗰d"},{"pid":"854bb47639a9681a5c592666f6b9c3d4df5c6000","tid":796920,"uid":13953,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T06:07:42.000Z","msg":"Part time就算把啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大公司Intern就話姐"},{"pid":"0b22f156c4543c674264626bbf56f00666009a8a","tid":796920,"uid":126100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T06:08:34.000Z","msg":"咪話冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n垃圾part time 邊會理你"},{"pid":"239aa916b4891f7f2e91333133e705ca91c37cc1","tid":796920,"uid":58069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T06:15:11.000Z","msg":"因為之前追post 見到有巴絲寫左冇工作證明既PT入去,結果比人狂要求工作證明。但係個POST又冇左後話唔知佢點解決。<br />\n其實我諗住就咁照寫,佢要求就答冇就算。<br />\n稅單糧單果陣冇留，呢家搞番會唔會太煩,都幾年前"},{"pid":"90c14c9ac07f71ba88776436cfe198994dae1ad3","tid":796920,"uid":58069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ca63d80bf36957e4b29824d4dde035d60dd9a1e","tid":796920,"uid":61766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T06:07:24.000Z","msg":"你返part time 嗰陣無問佢攞工作證明？<br />\n有無糧單嗰d"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T06:17:04.000Z","msg":"冇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n糧單都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"773958f70e9aa47f537bbcda1e4347b65ee9baf7","tid":796920,"uid":196321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90c14c9ac07f71ba88776436cfe198994dae1ad3","tid":796920,"uid":58069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ca63d80bf36957e4b29824d4dde035d60dd9a1e","tid":796920,"uid":61766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T06:07:24.000Z","msg":"你返part time 嗰陣無問佢攞工作證明？<br />\n有無糧單嗰d"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T06:17:04.000Z","msg":"冇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n糧單都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T06:18:27.000Z","msg":"返工輪更表,銀行月結單入面? 例如7仔點都有credit個位寫住係dairy farm入錢比你啦掛? 如果你份PT係出票就無野講了"},{"pid":"b31122af78263c5eb7ea518afe49cd5ef8328e84","tid":796920,"uid":58069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b22f156c4543c674264626bbf56f00666009a8a","tid":796920,"uid":126100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T06:08:34.000Z","msg":"咪話冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.g